{"attribution":"Federal Trade Commission, Heads Up: Stop. Think. Connect., Simplified Chinese, August 2023; no FTC endorsement or affiliation is implied.","cases":[{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-001","input":"要在生活中帮助您的孩子安全上网，当心：停一停、想一想、问一问。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-001","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-002","input":"有一些想法可以帮助您与他们开始对话。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-002","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-003","input":"选择一节共同阅读，了解如何谨慎分享、友好在线、防范网络欺凌以及在线保护他们（和自己）的个人信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-003","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-004","input":"这些工具可以帮助您向孩子们展示如何做出正确的选择、负责任地使用科技。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-004","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-005","input":"通过交谈，您可以让孩子知道一旦他们犯了错误，有可以信赖的成年人会帮助他们。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-005","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-006","input":"上网是生活的一部分。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-006","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-007","input":"人们会在网上观看和创建内容、发布照片和视频、玩游戏、与朋友和家人分享自己所在的位置和所做的事情。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-007","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-008","input":"但在网上发布内容、娱乐和交流时会面临风险。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-008","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-009","input":"网上的某些人和情形并非总是真实可靠的。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-009","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-010","input":"无论手指在键盘、手机或平板电脑上移动得有多快，头脑和时间才是避免网络风险最好的工具。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-010","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-011","input":"停一停，认真想一想面临的情况可以帮助保护你自己、朋友和家人、你的账户和设备。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-011","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-012","input":"否则，最终可能会分享过多信息，让自己或他人尴尬，产生电脑故障，或者与戴着假面具的人交谈。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-012","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-013","input":"想要完全控制谁可以看到你的个人资料、图片、视频或文本是不可能的 — 即使用了在内容被查看后或在 24 小时内将其删除的隐私设置或应用软件也不可能完全控制。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-013","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-014","input":"任何看到你发贴的人都可以截图或录像。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-014","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-015","input":"问一下自己：“想不想让某人在午餐时与全餐厅的人分享那张照片或者那个视频？”","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-015","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-016","input":"你分享的事物可能影响到其他人。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-016","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-017","input":"未经当事人准许发送或发布照片和视频可能导致令人尴尬、不公平甚至不安全的状况。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-017","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-018","input":"首先征得当事人的同意。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-018","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-019","input":"发布前问一下他们：“您同意我在社交媒体上发布这个东西吗？”","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-019","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-020","input":"如果他们不同意，不要发布。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-020","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-021","input":"网上的行为会产生真实的后果。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-021","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-022","input":"分享的照片、视频和消息会影响你自己、你的隐私、你的声誉和周围的人 — 可能是现在，也可能是将来。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-022","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-023","input":"发贴前停一停，想一想。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-023","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-024","input":"即使你删除了已经发布的内容，或者发布已过期，你不想让人看到的照片或评论也可能被保存、分享或在网上的其他地方存在 — 而且永存。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-024","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-025","input":"发送色情信息：不要这样做。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-025","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-026","input":"你可能在学校或者新闻中听到过人们“发送色情信息” — 用其手机发裸照。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-026","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-027","input":"绝对不能这么做。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-027","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-028","input":"创建、转发甚至保存色情照片、视频或信息会使你面临失去友谊和声誉的风险。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-028","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-029","input":"更糟的是，你的行为还可能违法。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-029","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-030","input":"根据美国卫生部长的说法，使用社交媒体可能会对你造成伤害，具体取决于在社交平台上花费的时间，看到的内容类型，及其对人的健康至关重要的睡眠或锻炼等活动的干扰程度。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-030","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-031","input":"由于在网上看不到别人的面部表情、肢体语言或其他视觉线索，你可能会发布或说出不会当面说的话。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-031","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-032","input":"但发短信、发帖、直接消息、玩电子游戏和发电子邮件与面对面的交谈在实施上是一样的。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-032","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-033","input":"请注意自己的沟通方式，务必三思而后行。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-033","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-034","input":"网上容易产生误解。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-034","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-035","input":"在发送消息前，问自己: “其他人会对这条消息有什么感觉？”","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-035","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-036","input":"考虑并尊重他人在网上的看法和情感 — 就像面对面打交道一样。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-036","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-037","input":"记住：头像和个人资料名称背后都有真人。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-037","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-038","input":"不要全部使用大写字母，也不要用一连串的感叹号或粗大字体。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-038","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-039","input":"网上书写的这种风格就跟面对面大喊大叫一样没有区别。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-039","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-040","input":"不要把所有东西都放在群聊里。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-040","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-041","input":"在群发消息或点击“全部回复”前，停下来想一想：谁需要看到这条消息？","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-041","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-042","input":"冒充他人（例如同学或老师）创建个人资料、评论或发贴是错误的，甚至可能造成伤害。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-042","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-043","input":"如果看到朋友发送了轻率或不安全的内容，提醒他们。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-043","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-044","input":"你可以帮助朋友减少麻烦和难堪。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-044","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-045","input":"如果在网上看到不适宜的内容，报告并告诉可以信赖的成年人。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-045","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-046","input":"大部分应用软件和平台都有报告有危险或不当行为的途径。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-046","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-047","input":"无论是在网上还是实际生活中，每个人都有权利在与他人日常交流时有安全感。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-047","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-048","input":"如果有人发布刻薄的评论、伤人的表情包、尴尬的照片，或者发送关于你的聊天或私人信息，那就是欺凌。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-048","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-049","input":"欺凌是不当的行为。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-049","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-050","input":"向你信赖的成年人讲述这种情况，得到相应的帮助，并决定如何应对。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-050","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-051","input":"不理此人或将其拉黑。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-051","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-052","input":"保存记录并向可以信赖的成年人求助。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-052","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-053","input":"大部分应用软件和平台都有报告不当或危险行为的工具。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-053","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-054","input":"欺凌往往会让被骚扰的人感觉不好 — 也会让欺凌者形象不佳。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-054","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-055","input":"欺凌还可能导致校方或警方的介入。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-055","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-056","input":"如果你目睹了网络欺凌，想办法加以阻止 — 勇敢出面主持公道。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-056","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-057","input":"如果有人能出面帮助被欺凌的人，恶劣的行为通常很快就会停止。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-057","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-058","input":"网上任何行为都会留下痕迹。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-058","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-059","input":"通过以下步骤确保痕迹不会导致泄露不想分享的信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-059","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-060","input":"了解如何为设备、应用软件和社交媒体账户开启隐私设置 — 然后加以运用。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-060","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-061","input":"它可帮助限制谁能看到你所在的位置、所发的帖子以及谁能与你联系。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-061","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-062","input":"检查自己的位置设置。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-062","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-063","input":"有些应用软件能让用户看到其朋友所在的位置。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-063","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-064","input":"它们还能分享用户的位置。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-064","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-065","input":"想一想什么时候需要分享自己的位置。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-065","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-066","input":"如果不需要，关闭位置共享。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-066","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-067","input":"设备上的功能（如摄像头）可能有拍照时所在位置的信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-067","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-068","input":"如果不想每次自拍都让所有人看到自己的位置，请关闭手机摄像头上的位置功能。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-068","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-069","input":"每次都扪心自问：“这个应用软件需要知道我的位置吗？”","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-069","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-070","input":"将网友限制为自己生活中认识的人。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-070","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-071","input":"通过短信、社交媒体或电子游戏交朋友可能很有趣 — 但有些人的实际身份与网上身份大相径庭。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-071","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-072","input":"如果不小心，可能会与陌生人分享个人信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-072","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-073","input":"一旦给了陌生人自己的个人信息 — 例如社保号、密码或者银行账户信息，就没有办法再收回。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-073","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-074","input":"不要回复索要个人信息的邮件。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-074","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-075","input":"即使邮件像是来自认识的朋友、家人或公司 — 或者说不回复会有不好的后果也不要给出个人信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-075","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-076","input":"很可能它们是假冒的，想要窃取个人信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-076","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-077","input":"向可以信赖的成年人求助，将邮件报告为垃圾邮件。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-077","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-078","input":"在下载该应用软件前，检查应用软件想要访问的信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-078","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-079","input":"有些应用软件申请权限访问它们不需要的信息或功能，例如联系人列表、摄像头、存储、位置和麦克风。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-079","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-080","input":"请可以信赖的成年人帮助阅读应用软件的隐私政策，查看如何使用你的数据，以及是否会分享该数据。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-080","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-081","input":"然后确定那个文字游戏是否真需要访问你的照片。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-081","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-082","input":"在应用软件内购物之前先咨询可以信赖的成年人 — 尤其是在它们自行付费时务必先咨询成年人。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-082","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-083","input":"你的网上账户中有大量的个人信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-083","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-084","input":"下面这些步骤可以防止他人侵入你的账户。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-084","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-085","input":"密码越长，越难破解。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-085","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-086","input":"至少有 12 位字符，而且同时含有大小写字母、数字和符号。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-086","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-087","input":"考虑使用随机文字组成的密码短语，让密码不易忘记。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-087","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-088","input":"但不要使用常见的短语、歌词或电影台词，这些都很容易被猜测到。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-088","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-089","input":"使用独特的密码。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-089","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-090","input":"不同的账户使用不同的密码。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-090","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-091","input":"这样，如果有人得到了一个账户的密码，他们无法入侵其他账户。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-091","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-092","input":"可以使用密码管理器来跟踪所有不同的密码。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-092","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-093","input":"不要与任何人分享密码，即使是最好的朋友或恋人。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-093","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-094","input":"精心挑选安全问题。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-094","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-095","input":"尽量选择只有自己能回答的安全问题。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-095","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-096","input":"不要选择其他人可以在网上找到答案的问题 — 例如，自己的邮政编码、出生日期或母亲的闺名。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-096","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-097","input":"如果无法避免这些问题，发挥创意！","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-097","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-098","input":"将它们当成密码，使用随机的长答案。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-098","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-099","input":"但要确保自己能记住答案。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-099","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-100","input":"使用多重身份验证。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-100","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-101","input":"许多账户通过使用“多重身份验证”为账户提供更多保护— 除了密码，还需要其他验证。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-101","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-102","input":"多重身份验证将你知道的事物（例如密码）和你有的事物（例如应用软件生成的密码）或你自身（例如指纹）组合到一起。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-102","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-103","input":"如果密码泄露，请迅速更改。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-103","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-104","input":"如果公司通知你出现数据泄露，黑客可能得到了你的密码，请迅速更改该账户密码。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-104","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-105","input":"同时更改任何使用类似密码账户的密码。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-105","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-106","input":"什么是最好的在线体验方式？","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-106","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-107","input":"确保自己设备的安全。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-107","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-108","input":"将所有设备、互联网浏览器和操作系统的安全软件设置为自动更新。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-108","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-109","input":"这样有助于防范新的安全威胁。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-109","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-110","input":"不要点击链接或打开附件。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-110","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-111","input":"如果在网上收到陌生的短信、电子邮件或消息，要你点击链接或打开附件，切勿听信！","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-111","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-112","input":"即使是免费优惠卷也不要上当。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-112","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-113","input":"链接和附件可能隐藏病毒或间谍软件，它们可能会入侵你的手机、电脑或平板电脑。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-113","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-114","input":"用密码保护设备。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-114","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-115","input":"这将有助于防止照片、消息和帐户落入坏人之手。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-115","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-116","input":"将它们存放在安全的场所。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-116","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1/sentence-117","input":"无论是手机、台式机还是平板电脑，都不要把它留在公共场所 — 即使是只有片刻。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/792A_Heads%20Up%20Stop%20Think%20Connect_Chinese-Simplified_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-117","split":"booklet"}}],"converter_output_used":false,"dataset":"blind-v2","id":"ftc-heads-up-simplified-v1","input_only":true,"license":"U.S. Public Domain","modification_notice":"Extracted only complete Simplified Chinese prose sentences from the checksum-pinned FTC-authored PDF, joined PDF layout wraps and cross-page sentences, removed headings, page furniture, English parallel text, navigation URLs, and incomplete fragments, and added input-only provenance; no images, seals, expected text, or converter output were used.","purpose":"candidate_source_pilot","review_policy":"domain_and_risk_must_be_assigned_from_input_only","source_class":"public_domain","stats":{"by_split":{"booklet":117},"eligible_pending_review":117,"exclusions":{},"raw_cases":117},"upstream_revision":"FTC Heads Up: Stop. Think. Connect., Simplified Chinese, August 2023; PDF Last-Modified 2024-02-28T20:57:23Z; raw SHA-256: fd48b428794f5a70b32da3d56f264149963b68d8b9382a8fedf1c434d3a01112","version":1}
